        <consumer>RULE</consumer>
        <consumer>SCHEDULE</consumer>
      </expose-to>
      <documentation>
        <description>Reset VM
    Shuts down the guest OS and restarts it. This operation depends on the OS being shut down. Note: If shutdown is not automatic for that OS, VMware Tools must be installed.</description>
